"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"bulletItem\">",
"     <a class=\"graphic graphic_diagnosticimage\" href=\"UTD.htm?6/43/6832\" title=\"diagnostic image 4\">",
"      Transverse fracture of the 5th metacarpal shaft",
