"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10028136\">",
"      What is this drug used for?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10028135\">",
"      What do I need to tell my doctor before I take this drug?",
"     </a>",
